Attributes.Label: About Me
Attributes.Value: Hi! HI HI HI! Did ya hear me? Oh, good. I'm Mookie, or Blossom, or whatever you'd like! I'm a talkative and outgoing full grown lady of nearly 7 years.  I'm pretty set in my ways but still optimistic for a home and family that would suit me! I really don't like other dogs and it's unlikely that I'll like cats any better. Respectful and savvy children would probably be alright but I can be a little off-putting sometimes so no-one too timid or faint of heart, kay? I'm ready for walks, naps, adventures abound! Let's get a move on! there is so much to see and do! So many beds left un-napped in! Come meet me today!

Attributes.Label: About Me
Attributes.Value: Hello! I'm Fonora! I'm an adorable 4 year old girl who is so tired of being lonely! I have many positive qualities that seem to be going overlooked. I am petite and energetic. I love to go on walks! The world might be a big scary place but I'm not gonna let it keep me down! I wanna bounce right alongside you and face all our problems together! Unless it's dogs. I don't want to face any dogs. I don't like them. I've never met a cat, not sure if I want to. If you're not a dog I'm sure we'll get along great. I really enjoy giving hugs! You'll have to see it to believe it! We'll be an unstoppable duo but you have to come meet me to get that duo started! See you soon!

Attributes.Label: Additional Info.
Attributes.Value: Return...No bite/scratch. Housetrained, Owner took dog camping and had around 2 other small dogs and was very leash reactive to other dogs.

Attributes.Label: About Me
Attributes.Value: Pumpkin here! I'm a 12 year old lady with a lifetime of wisdom behind me and one full of love awaiting me. I'm just looking for the right person to spend that time with, and I really hope it's you! My previous owner said that I have never met a dog and I don't do well around kids or other cats. I would do best in a quiet, calm environment where I can relax and enjoy my golden years. I enjoy basking in the sun and getting lots of daily love and attention. Age is nothing but a number, and even though I may be considered a senior cat, my heart is still young and full of love. Adopt me today!

Attributes.Label: Additional Info.
Attributes.Value: ORE for behavior; attacked/scratched children multiple times unprovoked.

Attributes.Label: Additional Info.
Attributes.Value: Stray cat found on property, microchipped, patchy hairloss on head,

Attributes.Label: About Me
Attributes.Value: Howdy!!! My name is Snickerdoodle and I am one cool cat! I was found as a stray and folks don't know much about my history but I can tell you that I am very snuggly, would make a great lap kitty, pretty chatty and may follow you around the house if you like! I would do well in a home with children but have not been exposed to dogs or cats. Please come and meet me to see if I am the snicker to your doodle!

Attributes.Label: About Me
Attributes.Value: Greetings mortal! I am Caliban but I am no monster of myth and legend. I am a simple man of 6 years looking for a home to call my own. I don't want to live in a fishy cave in the woods ever again. I am a very unique man and am very much looking forward to meeting the people that can love me for the rest of my days. Is it you? Can you come meet me? Can we be family?

Attributes.Label: Additional Info.
Attributes.Value: FINDER HOLD. Finder found in a persons back of truck who found the cat in a laundry bin. No bite/scratch. Friendly

Attributes.Label: About Me
Attributes.Value: Hi my name is Molly!!! I am such a sweetheart and love to snuggle under my cat bed! I feel safe and cozy under there! I need a quiet home to go to and to only be around older children who can take it slow wiith me. I would make a great couch kitty just lounging around with you! Come in and see how sweet I am!

Attributes.Label: About Me
Attributes.Value: Hello good sir or madam, my name is Goodfellow, Robin Goodfellow that is. I am a very quiet gentleman and I enjoy spending my days relaxing in the sun while keeping a watchful eye on the birds and squirrels of the outside world. I can be a little shy when meeting new people, but after some chin scratches and sweet talk, I come around quickly and become your best friend. If you're looking for a cat who really is a good fellow, I'm your guy. Come in and take me home today!

Attributes.Label: About Me
Attributes.Value: Johnson!!! That's me! I am the cutest dog you have ever laid eyes on (or so I'd like to think) and I am ready to be welcomed into your home so I can start my new life. I'm still a young pup, so I have lots of energy and need to go to a home where I can get daily exercise to burn that energy off. We could go for walk, or hikes, or play fetch, I mean the possibilities are just endless! We could be great pals and do almost everything together! Now that summer is here, the sunny days are perfect for outside adventures, so come in and adopt me so we can start our life together!

Attributes.Label: About Me
Attributes.Value: Howdy doody there. I'm Gunderson. Son of Gunder. Whomever that is. Not exactly sure. I'm about 2 years old and was found wandering near an Ikea. Like their products, I'm a bit odd and a little interesting to deal with but overall, I'm a nice young man who just wants a loving and quiet home where I can slowly open up and be the best cat I can be. New things are very stressful and with time I can adjust as well as any. Come meet me today!

Attributes.Label: Additional Info.
Attributes.Value: Found in White Marsh Ikea. Possibly came in on a truck.

Attributes.Label: Additional Info.
Attributes.Value: Owner Surrender (Allergies) Main Coon X came in with Milo, no concerns

Attributes.Label: About Me
Attributes.Value: I am Tigger! I am a fluffy, 2 year old bundle of love. My previous home said I was a very social and outgoing young man and that I got along tolerably well with cats, dogs, and children! Even strangers, if they give me time to adjust to their presence. Loud noises of course make me jump and run and hide but that's just natural! Overall I'm a laidback and tolerant boy who is just so excited to make your acquaintance.

Attributes.Label: Additional Info.
Attributes.Value: Owner surrender (Allergies) Main Coon X, Came in with Tigger, no concerns

Attributes.Label: About Me
Attributes.Value: I am Milo! I am a floofy, 2 year old bundle of energy. Family members in my past indicated that I got along tolerably well with cats, dogs, and children! It takes a minute to adjust but I like to think I’m a fairly easygoing boy who is inquisitive and social. But everyone’s got an opinion. Yours will probably coincide with mine. Let’s face it, I’m awesome. Come meet me today!

Attributes.Label: About Me
Attributes.Value: Sharon, Sharon, SHARON!!!  Oh hey, you're gonna have to speak up youngin'.  I'm not as young as I once was but I'm still a great kitty.  I've worked hard my whole life and I'm ready to just kick back and relax, can I do that in your home? I will lounge and purr and blink at you but ya gotta give an old lady like meself some time to adjust, can I do that in your home? Great. Let's kick it.

Attributes.Label: Additional Info.
Attributes.Value: ore- daughter is surrendering deceased mothers cat. the cat scratched her on 6/11 and is not friendly. the fire dept. had to remove the cat from a wall inside of the mothers home. the cat is blind and hasn't been eating.

Attributes.Label: About Me
Attributes.Value: Hey everyone! I'm Egypt 8. I'm a cute little kitty who needs a quiet, loving home with someone who is patient in waiting for me to warm up to them. I would love a bed near the window so I can enjoy a nice, quiet sunny spot. I'm someone who likes to be alone most of the time, so I would not be a good fit with other cats or dogs. But I would love to be your companion, so come on over and meet me!

Attributes.Label: About Me
Attributes.Value: Hi new people! I'm Egypt 14, a quiet, sweet little girl who would love a calm home with someone who can give me endless love and cuddles. I'm pretty independent, so I may not do well with other animals or small children. While I may take a while to warm up to you, I'm extremely hopeful we can get there! I just need a bunch of TLC and plenty of treats and toys, and we'll be on our way to being the greatest of friends! So why not give me a chance and take me home today!

Attributes.Label: About Me
Attributes.Value: Well hello there! I was just dreaming of what it would be like to find my permanent home and how I would spend my days there. I would love a home that is nice and quiet without young kids, where I can just relax and do my own thing. I would sun bathe in the window and then move to the couch, and when I decide it's time for my daily pets I will find my human and rub up against them. I'm a very sweet boy, but I am also very shy, so I need a home that will be patient with me while I adjust to my new surroundings. I know that with proper love and care I will be the best kitty you've ever had, so please come adopt me and make all my dreams come true!

Attributes.Label: About Me
Attributes.Value: The sun is shining, the birds are chirping, and it is a perfect day to come adopt a cat. My name is Smoke and I am a 1 year old kitty on the search to find my new family that will take me to my new home. I am still adjusting to my new environment here at the shelter, so I am very shy and unsure of things. I would do best in a home where I can have my own space and time to adjust, with someone who is willing to be patient and understanding of my needs. I also prefer a home with no young children, where it is quiet and relaxing. I have lived with other cats and did well with them, so if you already have a feline at home, that might help to make my transition easier. I'm really just a sweet boy in need of a home that's the right fit for me, so please come to meet me and see if that home is yours!

Attributes.Label: Additional Info.
Attributes.Value: For the past few months Annabelle has been chewing her tail and causing injury to herself. The tail bleeds constantly and owner does not know what caused her to start doing this. The cat is very afraid and likes to keep to herself.

Attributes.Label: About Me
Attributes.Value: So. Hi. I suppose I should keep working on my manners. My name is Annabelle and I am about 8 years old.  I desire a home of my own, nice and quiet. No kids or cats or dogs please. I want lots of perches and towers and windows and places to call my own. I'm an independent type lady who wants to do things my way and in my own time. Don't I just sound divine? Darn right I am. Let's get me settled in your home today!

Attributes.Label: Additional Info.
Attributes.Value: Neighbors believe cat was put outside by owners after they were evicted around a year ago.  Various residents have been feeding the cat and say that it is very friendly and always tries to run inside people's homes.  I was able to pick cat up and put in carrier.

Attributes.Label: About Me
Attributes.Value: Hi there! I am the friendly and sassy Gingersnap! I'm a dignified 4 year old lady. I do what I want when I want and need a family willing to accept me doing that and needing my own space. I will approach for love but need you to watch for signs when I've had enough. I love to be watched and talked to very sweetly and I bet I would make your home even more lovely and graceful by my mere presence! So come on in and meet me today!

Attributes.Label: About Me
Attributes.Value: Hi there! I am Catalina and I am adorable. I am a lovely young girl with striking good looks that should be the envy of every cat out there. I'm sleek, I'm stately, I have gorgeous green eyes. I'm the perfect example of felinity. I even chat a little bit if I have something to say!  So come on in and meet me today. I bet you'll fall in love faster than you can say my name. Try it!

Attributes.Label: Additional Info.
Attributes.Value: Owner adopted cat from Petco (they were housing cats from Last Chance Animal Rescue) and they were told that she was spayed and vaccinated. A few days after getting her home they suspected that she was pregnant and 2 months ago she delivered 4 kittens. They have found placement for 3 but one they have not been able to. Owner's other 2 cats are not getting along with Catalina so she is surrendering her and her 1 kitten today.

Attributes.Label: Additional Info.
Attributes.Value: owner is surrendering because she is moving

Attributes.Label: About Me
Attributes.Value: Hey new friends! I’m Bex Ra, a beautiful and friendly girl who’s looking for her fur-ever home. I’m very independent, but when I’m in the mood, I love attention. My previous owners say I am good with cats and take a bit of time to warm up to dogs, but overall, I’m a great catch! I mostly love to just lounge in my bed with blankets, but there’s always time to play with toys! If you think you can provide a life full of love and happiness, stop by today to see me!

Attributes.Label: Additional Info.
Attributes.Value: Stray cat at BARCS, has chip that traces to impound #2688 from 2017

Attributes.Label: About Me
Attributes.Value: Hello there! I am Walstocka! I'm a super laid back and relaxed gentleman. I'm about 2 years old. I have lived a time in the big wide world and am heartily sick of it. I would most like a soft and tall perch from which to watch the goings-on of your, soon to be my, household.  I have all the qualifications of a housecat. I'm a cat, I want to be in your house, what more can you ask? I purr, I lounge, I saunter, I look distinctly uninterested even while intently learning and observing everything around me. Come meet me today!

Attributes.Label: Additional Info.
Attributes.Value: No bite/scratch. No finder hold. Seem friendly. Found outside finders house 2 days ago roaming around on property.

Attributes.Label: About Me
Attributes.Value: Hello there. I'm Mum Boo and mum's the word on my previous experiences! I'm a grown lady of 8 years and I've seen quite a bit of the world but I ain't talking about it. I'm just gonna ready myself for new experiences and memories. I've got lots of time to make ‘em and I'd like your help to do so. I'm a very sweet girl who doesn't like to be startled but enjoys being petted.  A nice quiet home full of calm people would be the best. The kind of people with active hands and would let me wander between pettings. I bet you're the best at petting. Come meet me today!

Attributes.Label: Additional Info.
Attributes.Value: No bite/scratch. No finder hold. Found w/ mum boo outside roaming on the finders property for 2 days.

Attributes.Label: About Me
Attributes.Value: Good morning to you! I'm Tulip Boo but I'm no spring chicken. I'm an 8 year old lady and unsure how I found myself in this predicament! It's all so confusing and new! But sort of exciting too... Anyways I think I would best enjoy a household with peace and quiet and space for me to be myself. Patient people with the knack of being around a timid cat would be just perfect for me! Come meet me today and we'll see how we get along, eh?

Attributes.Label: About Me
Attributes.Value: Hi there! I'm Dixie and let me tell you I'm ready to start whistling! I'm done with this shelter stuff and ready to come out into your world! I'm a bit of a wanderer and need some people to help settle me down. I love to chat and sing and snuggle and wiggle! I do not like other cats. I'm not real sure how I feel about being around children or dogs. I'm ready to meet you and get started on the rest of my life. Come meet me today!

Attributes.Label: Additional Info.
Attributes.Value: Cat likes to escape out the door frequently and is now pregnant. This is her 2nd time being pregnant and owner is not able to care for. Cat does not get along with the other cats they have at home and needs to go to a home where she is the only feline.

Attributes.Label: Additional Info.
Attributes.Value: Owner recently passed away and her son is not able to take care of the cats so he is surrendering them to us as the owner.

Attributes.Label: About Me
Attributes.Value: Hello!! My name is Smudge Pal and I came in with my housemate, Smokey Pal! It would be awesome if we could go home together since we are very bonded. I am a little timid but if you go slow with me I will open up and be a super sweet cuddle bug. I would do best in a calm, quiet home with no young children please. Come out and meet me!

Attributes.Label: About Me
Attributes.Value: Hello!!! My name is Smokey Pal and I came in with my housemate Smudge Pal! It would be awesome if we could go home together since we are very bonded. I am a little timid but if you go slow with me I will open up and be a super sweet cuddle bug! I would do best in a calm, quiet home with no young children please! Come out and meet me!

Attributes.Label: Additional Info.
Attributes.Value: Owner recently passed away and her son is not able to take care of the cats so he is surrendering them to us as the owner.
